SQL_STMT_U.val: select * from PRD005 where E_TYPE=':1' and E_NO=:2

Text.valUnicode:
Frame & Engine Information in PRD005 Table is stored in following way:
Row1 -> Frame Number, Engine Number Row2 -> Engine Number, Frame Number
During Af-Off, Frame Number is united against Engine Number and vice versa.

Utility works to find all data mismatch for Row 2 option.
Following process is used:
> Find Engine Number with blank Frame Number. > Find Frame Number for above Engine Number. > Update Frame Number against the Engine Number.
